{"name":"breadcrumb","versionType":"4.4-jsx","type":"components","group":"components","basename":"breadcrumb.md","relpath":"4.4-jsx/components/breadcrumb.json","attributes":{"layout":"docs","title":"Breadcrumb","description":"Indicate the current page's location within a navigational hierarchy that automatically adds separators via CSS.","group":"components"},"html":"<h1 class=\"bd-title\" id=\"content\">Breadcrumb</h1><p class=\"bd-lead\">Indicate the current page's location within a navigational hierarchy that automatically adds separators via CSS.</p><h2 id=\"example\">Example</h2>\n<div class=\"bd-example\" id=\"mvvm_typeb3700cbe0faa222bb2993676231150c5\" data-mvvm-type=\"mexample_with_code\">\n</div>\n\n<script type=\"text/plain\" data-js-id=mvvm_typeb3700cbe0faa222bb2993676231150c5>\nvar Sample = function () {\n  return (\n    React.createElement( React.Fragment, null,\n      React.createElement( Breadcrumb, null,\n        React.createElement( Breadcrumb.Item, { active: true, 'aria-current': \"page\" }, \"Home\")\n      ),\n      React.createElement( Breadcrumb, null,\n        React.createElement( Breadcrumb.Item, null, React.createElement( 'a', { href: \"#\" }, \"Home\") ),\n        React.createElement( Breadcrumb.Item, { active: true, 'aria-current': \"page\" }, \"Library\")\n      ),\n      React.createElement( Breadcrumb, null,\n        React.createElement( Breadcrumb.Item, null, React.createElement( 'a', { href: \"#\" }, \"Home\") ),\n        React.createElement( Breadcrumb.Item, null, React.createElement( 'a', { href: \"#\" }, \"Library\") ),\n        React.createElement( Breadcrumb.Item, { active: true, 'aria-current': \"page\" }, \"Data\")\n      )\n    )\n  )\n}\n;ReactDOM.render(React.createElement( Sample, { uuid: 'b3700cbe0faa222bb2993676231150c5' }), document.getElementById('mvvm_typeb3700cbe0faa222bb2993676231150c5'));</script>\n\n<div class=\"bd-clipboard\">\n                    <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-sample-collapse\" title=\"\" data-original-title=\"Toggle the sample\">\n                        Toggle\n                    </button>\n                    <button type=\"button\" class=\"btn-clipboard\" title=\"\" data-original-title=\"Copy to clipboard\">\n                        Copy\n                    </button>\n                </div><figure class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-jsx\">\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">Sample</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">active</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-current</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>page<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Home</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Home</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">active</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-current</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>page<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Library</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Home</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>a</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">href</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Library</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>a</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n        </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">active</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">aria-current</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>page<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">Data</span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb.Item</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n      </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span><span class=\"token class-name\">Breadcrumb</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span><span class=\"token plain-text\">\n    </span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n</code></pre>\n</figure>\n<h2 id=\"changing-the-separator\">Changing the separator</h2>\n<p>Separators are automatically added in CSS through <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/::before\"><code>::before</code></a> and <a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/content\"><code>content</code></a>. They can be changed by changing <code>$breadcrumb-divider</code>. The <a href=\"https://sass-lang.com/documentation/functions/string#quote\">quote</a> function is needed to generate the quotes around a string, so if you want <code>&gt;</code> as separator, you can use this:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$breadcrumb-divider</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token function\">quote</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\">\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n</figure>\n<p>It&#39;s also possible to use a <strong>base64 embedded SVG icon</strong>:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$breadcrumb-divider</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token url\">url</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token property\">data</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>image/svg+xml<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>base64<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>PHN2ZyB4bWxucz0iaHR0cDovL3d3dy53My5vcmcvMjAwMC9zdmciIHdpZHRoPSI4IiBoZWlnaHQ9IjgiPjxwYXRoIGQ9Ik0yLjUgMEwxIDEuNSAzLjUgNCAxIDYuNSAyLjUgOGw0LTQtNC00eiIgZmlsbD0iY3VycmVudENvbG9yIi8+PC9zdmc+<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n</figure>\n<p>The separator can be removed by setting <code>$breadcrumb-divider</code> to <code>none</code>:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><pre><code class=\"language-scss\"><span class=\"token property\"><span class=\"token variable\">$breadcrumb-divider</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> none<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre>\n</figure>\n<h2 id=\"accessibility\">Accessibility</h2>\n<p>Since breadcrumbs provide a navigation, it&#39;s a good idea to add a meaningful label such as <code>aria-label=&quot;breadcrumb&quot;</code> to describe the type of navigation provided in the <code>&lt;nav&gt;</code> element, as well as applying an <code>aria-current=&quot;page&quot;</code> to the last item of the set to indicate that it represents the current page.</p>\n<p>For more information, see the <a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria-practices/#breadcrumb\">WAI-ARIA Authoring Practices for the breadcrumb pattern</a>.</p>\n"}